reviewText: WELL MY HUSBAND AND MY TASTE IN MOVIES ARE VERY DIFFERENT. HE LOVED THESE MOVIES. I'M A FEMALE SO TO ME THEY WE'RE OK. BUT MOST OF US FEMALES DON'T GET INTO THESE MOVIES.
